affiliation.name: County of San Diego Communications Office

articleContent: Meet this week’s pet of the week, Garbo! Garbo is a very social and friendly former stray who is looking for a loving home. In her spare time, she enjoys being pet and finding new places to climb. If you’re interested in adopting Garbo, please visit www.SDDAC.com.
